				\begin{document}$$\mu \ne 0$$\end{document}μ≠0. However, this goal is arguably undermined by the fact that the value \documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
				\usepackage{wasysym} 
				\usepackage{amsfonts} 
				\usepackage{amssymb} 
				\usepackage{amsbsy}
				\usepackage{mathrsfs}
				\usepackage{upgreek}
